data.description: Enjoy sitting on the large welcoming porch of this classic Hillcrest Craftsman home !  Approx. 1682 sf with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Large living room with decorative fireplace leads to a large dining room to the kitchen.  Kitchen has a quaint nook for an open pantry or cozy eating area.  Beautiful original hardwood floors throughout and tiled bathrooms.  Backyard is fully fenced with a back covered porch and courtyard.  There is also a storage building with an adjacent room with a window unit that has potential for a studio, office, exercise or storage room.  Parking pads off the back alley.
